    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) is below required level due to single test condition; risk accepted given standardized ASTM F1717 protocol. E/uval < 1.96 for all QoIs. The independent numerical simulation cross-check for stiffness and yield force demonstrated inter-solver agreement within 1.8%, which the assessment team considered functionally equivalent to a second experimental data point, providing additional confidence in the model predictions. Overall credibility is sufficient for Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence. Assessment accepted.",
